Oh. or what? You're gonna
hire somebody to kill me?

952
00:41:18.043 --> 00:41:19.875
Huh?

953
00:41:24.816 --> 00:41:26.432
(groans loudly)

954
00:41:26.467 --> 00:41:29.952
(panting loudly)

955
00:41:29.988 --> 00:41:32.789
Should I carve you up.

956
00:41:32.824 --> 00:41:36.508
or should I wait
and catch the wife?

957
00:41:36.544 --> 00:41:38.377
Oh. no.
(gasps)

958
00:41:38.413 --> 00:41:40.563
God. Oh. God.

959
00:41:40.598 --> 00:41:42.009
Maybe one day
when you're at work...

960
00:41:42.033 --> 00:41:44.934
- Son of a bitch!
- (both grunting)

961
00:41:45.987 --> 00:41:47.237
Aah!

962
00:41:47.272 --> 00:41:48.654
(yells)

963
00:41:58.767 --> 00:42:01.066
What'd you say?!

964
00:42:01.102 --> 00:42:03.052
You're gonna kill who? Huh?

965
00:42:03.088 --> 00:42:04.754
Who you gonna kill?!

966
00:42:04.789 --> 00:42:06.956
Huh?! Huh?!

967
00:42:09.010 --> 00:42:10.426
Kill who?!

968
00:42:40.258 --> 00:42:42.258
(panting)

969
00:42:44.662 --> 00:42:46.645
♪ ♪

970
00:43:04.649 --> 00:43:06.289
- (gunshot)
- (grunts)

971
00:43:07.252 --> 00:43:09.235
(guttural gasping)

972
